        .container
        .row
            .col-md-4.col-md-offset-4
            .panel.panel-default
                .panel-body
                .text-center
                    h3
                    i.fa.fa-lock.fa-4x
                    h2.text-center Forgot Password?
                    p You can reset your password here.
                    .panel-body
                    form#register-form.form(role='form' autocomplete='off' method='post')
                        .form-group
                        .input-group
                            span.input-group-addon
                            
                            input#forgetemail.form-control(style='width: 50%; margin-left:23%;' name='email' placeholder='email address' type='email')
                        .form-group
                        input.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.btn-block.forget(style='width:50%; margin:auto; display:block; ' name='recover-submit' value='Reset Password' type='submit')
                        input#token.hide(type='hidden' name='token' value='')
                        p.note(style='color: green; display:none') Email has been sent to your registered email

